<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-10-0424 </DOCNO><TEXT>To make possibilities and limits of energy policy in Bavaria clear, wehave to first determine the legal and administrative political frameworkin which energy policy can act on state level in a federative state likethe Federal Republic of Germany. Furthermore, we also must show the energy-politicalstarting conditions of our country which, within this framework, areof decisive importance to the Bavarian energy policy with its specialcentral points and concerns. Only with the knowledge of these frame conditionswe can evaluate the results which in my opinion, confirm the correctnessof our energy policy. Before all, however, an analysis of the presentenergy-political problems, tendencies and requirements is necessary which,after all, might jeopardize what has been achieved till today.</TEXT></DOC>